	=09
			<p>You=E2=80=99ve created your wort, pitched your yeast, and fermented i=
t. Now you=E2=80=99ve come back after a week or two to take your legendary =
lager or astonishing ale through the final step. The only thing standing be=
tween you and that first refreshing sip of crisp, bubbly beer is a good pri=
ming and bottle conditioning.</p>
<p>When it comes to priming your brew, understanding the ins and outs of pr=
iming sugar=E2=80=94the main component in priming solution=E2=80=94is essen=
tial to making sure your careful craftsmanship and hard work pay off.</p>
<p><img fetchpriority=3D"high" decoding=3D"async" class=3D"aligncenter size=
