<h2 id=3D"priming-sugar-formulas-for-sweet-success">Priming Sugar Formulas =
for Sweet Success</h2>
<p>Sure, you could use that handy priming sugar calculator. Or you could ta=
ke credit for every single step of the homebrewing process by doing the mat=
h yourself. Let=E2=80=99s take a look at the formulas for each of the three=
 popular primers.</p>
<p>The brewer=E2=80=99s rule of thumb for every five gallons of beer is:</p=
>
